DATA,	0	,#Number
	"Internal speed ( 0th speed )"	,#Title
	0		,#Min.
	15000		,#Max.
	0x00	,#Attribute		
	2	,#Type  Bit1:OK to use at gain adjustment Bit0:Used at gain adjustment
	"Setup unit [r/min]"
	"Desired running speed can be set."
	"This is effective when [Pr.31: Speed command seleciton] is '0 : [ Pr.00 : Internal speed ( 0th speed )]'."
	"Upper limit is limited by [Pr.3B: Upper speed limit]. "
#N0.01#########################################################################
DATA,1,"1st speed",0,15000,0x00,2
	"Setup unit [r/min]"
	"Speed in multi-speed running can be set. "
	"It is effective when [Pr.32: Operation mode seleciton] is set to 2-speed operation mode. "
	"Upper limit is limited by [Pr.3B: Upper speed limit]. "
