DATA,16,"1st acceleration time",0,30000,0x00,2
	"The change factor of output speed in acceleration can be determined"
	"Set by time for changing 1000r/min. "
	"Time can be incremented by 0.01 sec for below 3 sec, by 0.1 sec from 3 sec up "
	"to 30 sec exclusive, and by 1 sec from 30 sec upward. "
#N0.11#########################################################################
DATA,17,"2nd acceleration time",0,30000,0x00,2
	"The change factor of output speed in acceleration can be determined"
